---
const quickFacts = [
  { label: 'Configuration', value: '3 & 4 BHK ultra-luxury homes' },
  { label: 'Scale', value: 'G+49 towers with skyline presence' },
  { label: 'Amenities', value: '1 lakh+ sq ft lifestyle spaces' },
  { label: 'Address', value: 'Osman Nagar, Tellapur' },
];
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="scroll-mt-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-warm-white to-beige/30 py-16 md:py-24"
  aria-labelledby="about-heading"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-14">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="sticky top-24 rounded-3xl border border-gold/30 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] sm:p-8">
          <div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="h-px w-10 bg-gold" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted">About Sky49</p>
          </div>

          <h2 id="about-heading" class="font-serif text-4xl leading-tight text-charcoal md:text-5xl">
            Sky49 Hyderabad: luxury living with long-term location value
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted sm:text-base">
            Sky49 Tellapur is planned as an ultra-luxury residential address for buyers who want strong
            daily livability today and confident resale relevance tomorrow.
          </p>

          <dl class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
            {
              quickFacts.map((fact) => (
                <div class="rounded-2xl border border-stone/40 bg-warm-white/95 p-4">
                  <dt class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-muted">{fact.label}</dt>
                  <dd class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-charcoal">{fact.value}</dd>
                </div>
              ))
            }
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-stone/40 bg-white p-6 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] sm:p-8 md:p-10">
          <figure class="mb-7 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-stone/40 bg-beige/30">
            <img
              src="/3-1024x682.png"
              alt="Sky49 lifestyle architecture view"
              class="aspect-[16/10] w-full object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </figure>

          <div class="mb-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-stone/50 bg-warm-white px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-charcoal">
              Tellapur growth corridor
            </span>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-stone/50 bg-warm-white px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-charcoal">
              Premium high-rise living
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-muted">
            <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/90">
              <strong class="font-medium text-charcoal">Sky49 Hyderabad</strong> rises in
              <strong class="font-medium text-charcoal"> Osman Nagar, Tellapur</strong> within the city’s premium
              western corridor. It is positioned for buyers comparing <em>Sky49 floor plans</em>,
              <em> Sky49 location</em>, and <em>Sky49 price</em> against long-horizon lifestyle quality.
            </p>

            <p>
              The project narrative combines vertical scale with a full-time residence mindset: high-rise towers,
              curated amenities, and planning choices that prioritize privacy, circulation, natural light, and
              social infrastructure rather than only marketing visuals.
            </p>

            <p>
              Tellapur’s advantage is practical as much as aspirational, with routes toward ORR, Financial District,
              Gachibowli, and the Neopolis-Kokapet growth belt. That matters for families balancing work commute,
              school access, and long-term asset liquidity.
            </p>

            <p>
              From a due-diligence perspective, always verify latest
              <strong class="font-medium text-charcoal"> RERA and project disclosures</strong> before purchase. For
              current availability, unit matching, and payment structuring, combine this page’s
              <a href="#facts" class="text-gold underline-offset-4 hover:underline">quick facts</a>,
              <a href="#location" class="text-gold underline-offset-4 hover:underline">location section</a>, and
              <a href="#faq" class="text-gold underline-offset-4 hover:underline">FAQ</a>
              with a guided on-site walkthrough.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center">
      <a
        href="#contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-charcoal px-7 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white transition hover:bg-gold hover:text-charcoal"
      >
        Register EOI Now
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
